text.div: This value set includes codes from multiple codesets.

name: ObjectLifecycleEvents
description: This example FHIR value set is comprised of lifecycle event codes. The FHIR Actor value set is based on    DICOM Audit Message, ParticipantObjectDataLifeCycle;   ISO Standard, TS 21089-2017;
copyright: This is an example FHIR value set based on ASTM Standard, E1762-95 (2013) HL7 RoleClass OID 2.16.840.1.113883.5.110,          HL7 Role Code 2.16.840.1.113883.5.111, HL7 ParticipationType OID: 2.16.840.1.113883.5.90, HL7 ParticipationFunction codes at OID: 2.16.840.1.113883.5.88,          and HL7 Security and Privacy Domain Analysis Model roles classes.
